OL,3,CRyan Mason appointed as new head coach
OL,4,Cof West Bromwich Albion
OL,6,FRyan Mason has been appointed as West
OL,7,FBromwich Albion head coach, signing a
OL,8,Fthree-year contract with the Baggies
OL,9,Fahead of the new season.
OL,11,FThe 33-year-old former Tottenham
OL,12,FHotspur assistant coach replaces Tony
OL,13,FMowbray, who was sacked following a
OL,14,Fseries of disappointing results that
OL,15,Fmeant West Bromwich Albion finished
OL,16,Foutside the play-off places.
OL,18,FIt's his first ever managerial
OL,19,Fposition, but he does come into the
OL,20,Frole with a wealth of coaching
OL,21,Fexperience.
