OL,6,FAfter his playing career was cut short
OL,7,Fby injury, he has acted as a coach at
OL,8,FTottenham Hotspur since 2018- filling
OL,9,Fin as interim head coach twice and
OL,10,Fhelping Spurs win a first trophy in 17
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FIn a statement released by the club,
OL,14,Fchairman Shilen Patel said "We are
OL,15,Fdelighted to welcome Ryan to The
OL,16,FHawthorns as our new Head Coach".
OL,18,F"We have undertaken a thoughtful and
OL,19,Fexpansive search and Ryan always stood
OL,20,Fout to us among an incredibly strong
OL,21,Fgroup of candidates.
