OL,3,CRyan Mason appointed as new head coach
OL,4,Cof West Bromwich Albion
OL,6,FRyan Mason started his footballing
OL,7,Fcareer at Tottenham, where he stayed
OL,8,Funtil a transfer to Hull City in 2016.
OL,9,FThe following year he suffered a
OL,10,Ffractured skull in a match against
OL,11,FChelsea and was forced to retire from
OL,12,Ffootball at 26 years old.
OL,14,FAfter retiring from football as a
OL,15,Fplayer, Mason joined the coaching
OL,16,Fstaff at Tottenham in 2018. During his
OL,17,Fspell there, he became the youngest
OL,18,Fmanager of a Premier League team,
OL,19,Ftaking over at 29 after Jose Mourinho
OL,20,Fwas sacked in 2021.
