OL,6,FThat season, he lost the EFL Cup Final
OL,7,Fby a single goal to Manchester City.
OL,8,FHe oversaw five more games in charge,
OL,9,Fwinning three and losing two finishing
OL,10,F7th in the Premier League.
OL,12,FHe had a second spell as interim coach
OL,13,Fafter Antonio Conte left Spurs. In
OL,14,Fthat spell he won two games, drew one
OL,15,Fand lost three to finish outside of
OL,16,Fthe European places.
