OL,3,CRyan Mason appointed as new head coach
OL,4,Cof West Bromwich Albion
OL,6,FSince Ange Postecoglou's appointment,
OL,7,Fhe has acted as an assistant coach.
OL,8,FDuring his tenure, Spurs have had
OL,9,Fmixed success. But they did win the
OL,10,FEuropa League this season, and end a
OL,11,F17 year drought without a trophy.
OL,13,FWest Bromwich Albion will be hoping
OL,14,Fthat the new man can get the right
OL,15,Ffoundations in place ahead of the new
OL,16,Fseason, and get them fighting for
OL,17,Fpromotion come August.
